<br>
- you are expected to stay and help until the end unless something pretty bad happens. This is why you are expected to either not care what happens or ask in advance, so that pretty much the only reason to leave would be something so bad in the leader breaking their word it's worth screwing all the other players. You will take a reputation hit for leaving usually unless you have a pretty good reason.<br>
<br>
